	<!-- Deliberately a PLAIN library:
	     - no dependencies (a record needs nothing)
	     - NO spring-boot-maven-plugin. That plugin repackages into an executable
	       fat jar, which CANNOT be consumed as a dependency. A shared lib must stay
	       a plain jar. This is the one place we do NOT copy the services' <build>. -->
